46.1.hd_quote: Dedication in obscurity that is unexpectedly discovered.
46.1.behavioral_axis: Stay in the experience even when unseen; recognition comes later.
46.1.shadow_axis: Quits early because no one is watching.

46.2.hd_quote: A difficult and demanding nature that succeeds despite its behavior because of the depth of its talents.
46.2.behavioral_axis: Talent + embodiment convinces others even if the style is demanding.
46.2.shadow_axis: Entitled presence that expects reward before it’s earned.

46.3.hd_quote: A practical approach to good fortune that maintains the same patterns.
46.3.behavioral_axis: Keeps to what works; stays in the experience until complete.
46.3.shadow_axis: Lets others’ projections interrupt the flow → stalled success.

46.4.hd_quote: The ability, once recognized, to move rapidly from obscurity to influence.
46.4.behavioral_axis: Once seen, they externalize their experience and climb fast.
46.4.shadow_axis: Forgets allies after success; appears ungrateful.

46.5.hd_quote: The maintenance of proper rhythm that avoids radical divergence from successful patterns.
46.5.behavioral_axis: Honors the cycle that’s bringing luck but knows when to stop.
46.5.shadow_axis: Lets others’ projections trap them in a dying pattern.

46.6.hd_quote: The wisdom to secure one's identity through careful consideration of commitments.
46.6.behavioral_axis: Only enters experiences that will feed back value to the collective.
46.6.shadow_axis: Overextends and later must break promises.
